title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Your clever ability to deliver a message tactfully enables you to caution close friends about potentially risky behavior without being a buzzkill. Its usually difficult to play the role of a referee with people you love so dearly. But if someone has to think ahead today, it might as well be an even-tempered person like you. For example, you are the logical choice to be the designated driver while out with your pals because you prefer to be responsible for getting everyone home, rather than being left to wonder and worry. Safety doesnt happen by accident. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
